    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Valerius Ter<lb break="no" n="2"/>ti <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pup</abbr><ex>inia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>XV <expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXIIII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>tip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XIIII sibi et Ni<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">gr</supplied>o Valerio Ter<lb break="no" n="6"/>ti <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pup</abbr><ex>inia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>eiusdem qui fuit <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXVI <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>XIIII testamen<lb break="no" n="10"/>to fieri iussit <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Munatius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Anie<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/>heres et Nigellae <lb n="13"/>matri eorum <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente, schräg über Z. 7/8 gebrochen. Zeile 1: ER-Ligatur; Zeile 2: E klein, G klein auf Rahmung stehend; Zeile 3: letzt III auf Rahmen und außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes stehend; Zeile 5: R außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes; Zeile 9: N z.T. auf Rahmung stehend. Niger Valerius hat, wie von anderen oberitalischen Namen bekannt (vgl. Mommsen bei CIL 05, 07025), das cognomen Tertius an Stelle des praenomen.</p>
            </div>
